Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.96,0:00:30.45,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It's the end of the century. {20th probably}
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.45,0:00:35.79,Narrator,,0,0,0,,With parched hearts, \Npeople sought solace in religion
Dialogue: 10,0:00:35.79,0:00:42.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and clung to gods and Buddhas \Nin hopes of living bright and happy lives.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.32,0:00:46.20,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But where there is light, there is shadow.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.20,0:00:51.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shadows that gave off an evil radiance \Nloomed overhead,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.80,0:00:57.95,Narrator,,0,0,0,,spreading fear among the people \Nand violating freedom of religion.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.50,0:01:12.07,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Then, following the example of Buddhist monks, {lit: dressed in buddhist kesa (wearing an article of clothing in the same manner as a kasaya (i.e. draped over one shoulder)​) - but later he says it's loincloth so idk, probably means "dressed in buddhist fashion"}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.07,0:01:18.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,there appeared a loincloth-clad superhero of love and justice to stand against the heretical forces.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.27,0:01:23.35,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Her name was \N{\i1}Butt Attack Punisher Girl Gautaman!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.44,0:02:21.42,Note,,0,0,0,,[Amachi Mari (1951-...) = Japanese idol active in the 1970s]
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.44,0:02:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Amachi Mari-san, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.52,0:02:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.13,0:02:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to PR Academy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:27.42,0:02:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The faculty office asked me to come pick you up.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.37,0:02:33.49,Note,,0,0,0,,[Minami Saori (1954-...) = Japanese idol active in the 1970s]
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.37,0:02:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Minami Saori.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.49,0:02:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be roommates in the girls' dorm.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.77,0:02:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.18,0:02:40.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,She's cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:41.47,0:02:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You already know a bit \Nabout PR Academy, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.77,0:02:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.44,0:02:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,P-Perfect Religion Academy.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.82,0:02:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A fully residential junior and senior high school that trains the future leaders of every religion in the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.82,0:03:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. We've all left the secular world behind to study religion day and night.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.97,0:03:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You too will...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.05,0:03:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I don't have any grand ambitions, \Nlike becoming a world leader.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.07,0:03:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I only came because my father wanted me to.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.84,0:03:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I manage to become even a little like Mother Teresa, the missionary of love,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.09,0:03:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that'd be enough for me to be happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.92,0:03:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.77,0:03:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,From here on, we walk. \NAnd let's be hush-hush about the motorcycle, okay? {from the school administration}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.04,0:03:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.42,0:03:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari-chan, you're a Christian?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.41,0:03:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.85,0:03:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hindu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.85,0:03:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.77,0:03:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if our denominations are different,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.91,0:03:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.86,0:03:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we can become very good friends.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.87,0:03:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:41.02,0:03:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll carry your bag for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.48,0:03:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? No, I can carry that much myself...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.88,0:03:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.86,0:03:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, if I let you carry it, \Nthe bag'll break before we get to school. {??? idk why}{it's because she'd drag it all the way to the school}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.08,0:03:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No way... But it really is heavy.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.83,0:04:11.64,Note,,0,0,0,,[a play on the 1987 OVA {\i1}Devilman: The Birth{\i0}] {probably? fairly common name actually, maybe the devilman itself was parodying something with it, like utsu no miko}{I don't think it is, tanjou-hen is pretty common}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.84,0:04:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.65,0:04:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take your trunk to the girls' dorm, \Nand you head to the faculty office.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's down the hall and to the right.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.15,0:04:28.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,So this is where I'll be studying from now on.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.84,0:04:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce our transfer student.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.75,0:04:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Amachi Mari. \NPlease take care of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.05,0:04:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.86,0:04:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She's cute! \NMari, eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.92,0:04:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,As for your seat...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.43,0:04:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.93,0:04:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's an empty one next to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-san.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.44,0:04:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you around inside.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.31,0:04:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.31,0:04:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since elementary school, \NI've lived in mission school dormitories,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.69,0:05:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,so the only men I've ever talked to \Nwere my father and the caretaker.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.70,0:05:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There are so many boys here... \NI'm really scared!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.08,0:05:12.58,Thought,,0,0,0,,Eh?! A totally sheltered greenhouse girl, huh? \NI wonder if she'll be okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.58,0:05:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me a second!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.88,0:05:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, you're Amachi Mari-kun, \Nthe new transfer student, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.05,0:05:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.87,0:05:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we go to the cafeteria over there and talk some religion?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.68,0:05:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Talk about religion?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.56,0:05:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If you fall for pickup-lines like that, \Nyou're asking for trouble. {lit: you're misjudging}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.55,0:05:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl's a hardcore Catholic.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She has absolutely nothing to talk about with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.07,0:05:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Mari-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.57,0:05:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Minami Saori!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.06,0:05:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There are evil religious groups at this school too.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.38,0:05:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,To propagate their own sect, \Nthey'll stop at nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.97,0:05:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They use force to pressure people into converting, \Nso don't go tagging along with any weird characters.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.63,0:05:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.67,0:06:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.36,0:06:35.95,Note,,0,0,0,,{was about say this was a parody of Kurotengu from tobe isami, but when I checked, isami aired a year later, so I have no clue; perhaps something even older that isami itself was taking inspiration from, maybe it's simply a traditional motif}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.36,0:06:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Black Buddha shall claim Minami Saori!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.67,0:06:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.85,0:06:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,S-She's been kidnapped! What do I do?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.00,0:06:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Holy Mary...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.74,0:06:48.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,Lord, what should I do?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.93,0:06:52.08,Thought,,0,0,0,,Please guide your humble servant.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.44,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Lord...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.62,0:07:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mindfulness... {????? R1 had "Mercy!"; nothing in manga}{むげ?}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.12,0:07:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Buddha.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.57,0:07:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The enlightened one, Buddha.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.82,0:07:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Also known as Gautama Siddhartha.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Buddha here? {and not christian god she was praying to}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.88,0:07:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall hear thy wish.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.48,0:07:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a Christian. \NWhy hasn't Lord Jesus{-sama} come?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.50,0:07:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the Virgin Mary?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.55,0:07:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,All things in this world are transient. \NForm is emptiness. {matter is void; all is vanity​}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.52,0:07:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't really understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.02,0:07:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, don this garment created from \NBuddha's own robe, and transform into Gautaman.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.48,0:07:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.75,0:08:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,The warrior of Buddha, Gautaman.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.42,0:08:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't! How could I?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.40,0:08:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,My body and soul are devoted entirely \Nto my Lord Jesus Christ of Nazareth.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.64,0:08:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a devout Christian!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.33,0:08:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really afford to be so carefree?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.85,0:08:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take a good look at this.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.54,0:08:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you remain stubborn after seeing that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.45,0:08:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to lose! \NTransform into Gautaman and save her!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.80,0:08:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman! Gautaman! Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.58,0:08:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling, Minami Saori?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.71,0:08:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the evil cult everyone's been talking about, \Nthe one forcing conversions by violence!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We prefer to be called Black Buddha.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.87,0:09:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The teachings of our faith are higher than mountains and deeper than oceans.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.66,0:09:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the supreme ruler \Nentrusted with dominion over this academy.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.10,0:09:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the future leader \Nof the religious world itself!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.36,0:09:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a proud devotee of the Hindu gods!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.75,0:09:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die, I'll never submit \Nto some evil cult like yours!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.68,0:09:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Such useless bravado.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.63,0:09:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone says that at first, \Nbut let's see how long your willpower lasts.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.30,0:09:36.30,Note,,0,0,0,,[parody of 1973 manga "Terror Newspaper"; this guy is its protagonist]
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.30,0:09:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Get her, Brainwashed Fiend{majin here is supposed to be "sorcerer; genie; human with supernatural powers" but he's not a sorcerer or even a villain himself, just a normal person hypnotized to work for black buddha; brainwashing here means he's been brainwashed to be bad, so maybe "Brainwashed Fiend" would be better? since he's not doing any brainwashing himself} \NTerror Newspaper Man!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.30,0:09:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.40,0:09:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.76,0:09:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Minami Saori...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.06,Thought,,0,0,0,,God... Help me, Shiva!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.39,0:09:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{?}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.11,0:09:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What the hell is that gong and chanting? {round, hollow, wood block (vaguely fish-shaped, usu. with scales), struck while chanting sutras}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.20,0:09:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.38,0:09:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as God and become God. {??? no idea what she means, not in manga; R1: "Be as god and become god"; I think she means "try to imitate god and you will become god"}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.78,0:10:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do as Buddha and attain Buddhahood. {seeing as she's barely wearing any clothes... just like buddha}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.17,0:10:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,By some strange karmic fate, I have been summoned, \Nand found myself wearing the sacred robes of Buddha.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.13,0:10:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,For those who force evil religions onto others \Nby violence cannot be forgiven!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.68,0:10:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand bastards like you!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.67,0:10:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Butt Attack Punisher Girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.93,0:10:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.27,0:10:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:29.52,0:10:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,In heaven's name, I shall punish evil!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.02,0:10:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourselves!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.66,0:10:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What a gorgeous... \Ner, I mean, cheeky little nuisance!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.29,0:10:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,To stand in the way of Black Buddha, who shall one day conquer the entire world's religious sphere...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.84,0:10:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You reckless fool!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.17,0:10:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't use religion for world domination!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.13,0:10:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Such wickedness will bring divine punishment \Nand send you straight to hell!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.79,0:10:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence! Whoever controls religion controls the world!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough chatter! Get her!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.88,0:10:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.68,0:11:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.68,0:11:06.53,Thought,,0,0,0,,Fear not, Gautaman! \NThou art strong!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.39,0:11:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.96,0:11:22.45,Top,,0,0,0,,Kyaa! I did it! I'm so strong! It's awesome!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.87,0:11:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That voice sounds kinda familiar...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.45,0:11:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you! What's more, how are you not ashamed of yourself, dressed like that?! {??? lit: down, that form/style, isn't it a violation - no clue what's that shita ga, maybe it's about her underwear, or rather it being the only thing she wears? no clue what it has to do with violation - violation of what, her religion maybe?}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what? {sugata = form/style}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.61,0:11:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.60,0:11:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! What kind of outfit is this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.95,0:11:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that? \NIsn't it a loincloth?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.46,0:11:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,A loincloth, all right. \NPerfect one at that.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.91,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah, this is so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.69,0:11:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Be not ashamed, Gautaman. {?? sounds like just gotan}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.52,0:12:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That loincloth is what awakens \Nthe cosmic power known as Kundalini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.69,0:12:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say that...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:02.33,0:12:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Your guard is down! {so that's why his name is newspaper of terror}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.25,0:12:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.22,0:12:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You let your guard down, Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.17,0:12:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure you regret defying us! {remember it}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.93,0:12:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.11,0:12:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If they take thy loincloth, \Nthy life is forfeit!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.80,0:12:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.44,0:12:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait, that's not fair!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.81,0:12:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.52,0:12:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you up to?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.83,0:12:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Brainwashed Fiend! \NRip her loincloth right off!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.42,0:12:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That goes without saying!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.23,0:12:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything but the loincloth, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.53,0:12:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Because{\i0} it's the loincloth, we can't show mercy!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.46,0:12:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{ara? maybe "oh no!"}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.75,0:12:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.22,0:12:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Gautaman...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.37,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid?! \NWhy would you tell the enemy her weak point?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.58,0:12:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you staring at?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Buddha-ya! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.43,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! It's tightening!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.04,0:13:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's your chance, Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.43,0:13:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The tighter Buddha's loincloth gets, \Nthe more power it unleashes!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.22,0:13:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.66,0:13:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!{korya}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.22,0:13:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:25.66,0:13:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There, Gautaman! Grab the front flap! \NYour ultimate weapon, the Gautama Folding Fan! {paper-covered folded fan used in noh and storytelling}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.42,0:13:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.60,0:13:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Brainwashing Fiend!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.62,0:13:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare yourself!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.85,0:13:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Take this then!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.61,0:13:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.89,0:13:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the Terror Newspaper!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.00,0:13:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A single read can shorten \Nyour lifespan by a hundred days!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.89,0:13:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.14,0:14:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen years of delivering newspapers—\Njust for them to be tossed aside the same morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:01.37,0:14:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think you can tear apart this secret technique \NI’ve perfected, go ahead and try! {yaburu as both "defeat" and "tear apart"}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.01,0:14:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What the... She tore it apart!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.63,0:14:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Terror Newspaper Man!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.80,0:14:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Religious conversion enforced through violence...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.86,0:14:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,even if Tsunoda Jiro-sensei could allow it,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.86,0:14:21.30,Note,,0,0,0,,[{parody of very typical tokusatsu confrontation speech; }{maybe this is obvious enough and doesn't need a note?}{it is obvious}Tsunoda Jiro (1936-...) = author of the {\i1}Terror Newspaper{\i0} manga]
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.75,0:14:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,this Gautaman will not!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.28,0:14:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit! Brainwashed Fiend's been defeated!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.57,0:14:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, hold up! You bastards \Nwere just pretending to be knocked out!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.57,0:14:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait! Don't leave me behind and run away!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.57,0:14:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Gautaman.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.11,0:14:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That loincloth actually suits you very well.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.26,0:14:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, farewell!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.24,0:14:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.03,0:15:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Lord, forgive me...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.86,0:15:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I devoted myself to serving the Lord, \NI had to obey Buddha. {instead of christ}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And if that wasn't enough,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.93,0:15:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I exposed my bare b-behind \Nin front of gentlemen! {tonogata = the men (3rd party)}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.55,0:15:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never go on living now!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.76,0:15:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Gautaman... \NYou'll pay for this!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.06,0:15:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.62,0:15:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.60,0:15:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:37.56,0:15:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.69,0:15:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Apparently a girl got abducted \Nfrom the dorm by Black Buddha,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.78,0:15:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but then a loincloth-clad \Nhero of justice saved her!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.03,0:15:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And get this, it was a girl too!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.32,0:15:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, rumors sure spread fast.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.12,0:15:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd need nerves of steel \Nto fight in a loincloth like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.65,0:16:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that "hero of justice" \Nmight actually just be some exhibitionist?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.20,0:16:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's secretly an aspiring porn actress? {AV }
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.40,0:16:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe some pervy old man?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.34,0:16:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.78,0:16:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, everyone's just saying whatever they want.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.84,0:16:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, you believe what I said about her true form, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.08,0:16:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mari?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.78,0:16:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.48,0:16:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Just a little anemic.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:24.07,0:16:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're seriously so frail. \NI can't take my eyes off you.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:28.10,0:16:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.57,0:16:34.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,Lord, I swear I will never, ever \Ntransform into Gautaman again.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.66,0:16:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A loincloth?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.60,0:16:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and apparently the pure white loincloth \Ndigs right into her cherry-blossom-colored skin!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.55,0:16:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not with Black Buddha, \Nbut even we'd like to see that at least once.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Cherry-blossom skin...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.46,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And pure white loincloth...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Digging right in...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.81,0:16:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the hero of justice \Nout of your lewd thoughts!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.73,0:17:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, Saori. \NIt's a nice rosy butt... with a loincloth!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You still don't get it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:05.22,0:17:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the one spreading these rumors?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.36,0:17:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Claiming some baseless \Nloincloth girl is a hero of justice...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.74,0:17:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not spreading anything. \NThe rumors are taking on a life of their own.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.11,0:17:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Then retract these lies!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.06,0:17:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Spreading malicious gossip \Nthat Black Buddha was defeated
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.94,0:17:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and tarnishing the cult's honor \Nwill not be tolerated, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.75,0:17:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not lies! I saw Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.51,0:17:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman? What's that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.26,0:17:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know not who she is, \Nbut with her graceful loincloth-clad form,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.98,0:17:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,her silky skin proudly exposed, \Nand that gaze hidden behind glasses,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.56,0:17:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone can tell she's a hero of justice!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.03,0:17:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneaking through this academy \Nto oppose the evil of Black Buddha...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.28,0:17:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,she is the invincible Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.03,0:17:57.43,Top,,0,0,0,,Wow, Gautaman? That's so cool... {??? no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.03,0:17:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Still going on about that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.38,0:17:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.79,0:18:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll have you know! We are... {charlie kirk}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.58,0:18:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Family mode! {??????? nothing in manga, was "running" in R1; I think I hear kazoku something?}{It's the accelerator device from Cyborg 009: https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/加速装置 but with 家族 instead of 加速; here's it in action: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0lBpTY5mJKU}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.58,0:18:05.96,Note,,0,0,0,,[parody of time-slowing device from Cyborg 009 \Nwith kasoku (acceleration) replaced for kazoku (family)]
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.96,0:18:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? N-No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.46,0:18:11.97,Note,,0,0,0,,[mutsugo = sextuplets; names on their uniforms \Ngo "Ichiro, Jiro, Saburo, ..." (1-ro, 2-ro, 3-ro, ...)] {R1 said it's a reference to https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Masanori_Hata - I think it's an asspull}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:07.46,0:18:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Same-egg sextuplet delinquents squadron! {sentai}\NThe Mutsugoros! Rings a bell?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.97,0:18:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.79,0:18:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Six totally identical faces!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.41,0:18:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No laughing!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.14,0:18:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The Brainwashed Fiend Sextuplets! {??? sounds like she knows them?}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.22,0:18:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You caught on too late!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.23,0:18:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! \NDon't be rough to her! Please stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.40,0:18:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If Gautaman really exists, then she ought to show up \Nand save you right here, you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.75,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's she doing, huh? \NMaybe she really is fake after all?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not fake! \NGautaman exists!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.37,0:18:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman is the savior \Nwho'll defeat you Black Buddha creeps!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.42,0:18:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're so sure, \Nthen let's have her come here!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.42,0:18:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:53.00,0:18:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, scream! \NCry out in despair.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.26,0:18:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If Gautaman exists, then call for her!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.64,0:19:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.19,0:19:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awful!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.18,0:19:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't anybody stand up to them?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.68,0:19:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Gautaman really exist?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.32,0:19:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't Gautaman come to save her?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.82,0:19:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.86,0:19:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she even real?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.86,0:19:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.20,0:19:26.21,Thought,,0,0,0,,Stop! Gautaman is gone now! \NI {Mari }swore to God I'd never transform again!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.21,0:19:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.97,0:19:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.42,0:19:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if it's a lie anymore! \NJust say it's all fake!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.96,0:19:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The sooner you say it, \Nthe better for you, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.54,0:19:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it with me, "I am a filthy liar."
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.72,0:19:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.90,0:19:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I believe in her.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.74,0:19:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a hero of justice, \Na warrior of love and hope.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.48,0:19:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.15,0:19:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.35,0:19:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you insist that much, then answer me this:
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.84,0:19:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why isn't your hero of justice showing up right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.31,0:20:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she scared of us?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.35,0:20:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And can a coward like that really be called \Na hero of justice, everyone?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.58,0:20:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This Gautaman is nothing but an idol she made up. {image/idealized picture}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.03,0:20:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So Gautaman is a fake, after all...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.75,0:20:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A loincloth on cherry-blossom skin...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,was but an illusion. {/dream}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.51,0:20:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman, come forth! {bringing about; giving rise to; causing; incurring}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.30,0:20:34.48,Note,,0,0,0,,{should we note that this is most likely parodying sailor moon? Naw, I suspect most people will get it. -PG}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.03,0:20:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,First point: Do you honestly think a young maiden \Nwould expose her butt in public like that, Jiro-kun? {2nd}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.07,0:20:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Shiro, actually. {4th}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:45.26,0:20:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, why don't we test it, Ichiro-kun? {1st}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.26,0:20:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm Saburo, Goro-kun. {3rd, 5th}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.71,0:20:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we test it?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.05,0:21:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.98,0:21:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What's this sutra chanting?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.51,0:21:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:07.23,0:21:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Minami disappeared!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.01,0:21:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Butt Attack Punisher Girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:12.15,0:21:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! She's real! {??? nandesune?}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.56,0:21:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:18.14,0:21:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.30,0:21:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure took your sweet time appearing! {lit: when you came it was late}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.82,0:21:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.44,0:21:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The chosen one, clad in the fated white loincloth, \Nshall stand upon the field of gold!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.70,0:21:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh! The prophecy was true! {Lady talking here is dressed as Obaba, the prophesier, from nausicaa of the valley of the wind}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.11,0:21:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She really is wearing a loincloth!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.45,0:21:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The savior truly exists! {fuck me this is toyotomi from super zugan}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.58,0:21:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's got an incredible figure too!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.69,0:21:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.34,0:21:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.06,0:21:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's blushing! {??? no clue, borrowing from R1}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.98,0:21:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:49.85,0:21:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't she cute? {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:52.16,0:21:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you do exist, this is as far as you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.46,0:21:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.61,0:21:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.56,0:22:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,For fifteen years, hidden away \Nin the Kingdom of Mutsugoro,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.94,0:22:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we perfected this ultimate technique \Nagainst animals. We call it...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,the Beast Mimicry Fist! {鳥獣擬人拳 = Animal Anthropomorphism Fist}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.65,0:22:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Tanuki are shy around people, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.66,0:22:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Rabbits like carrots, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.66,0:22:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Birds fly like this, you know. \NAmazing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:19.29,0:22:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There, look! Watch this! It's angry now. \NThis one is actually a cat, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:24.92,0:22:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Folding Fan Crush!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:28.67,0:22:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She crushed them! \NShe's strong! Our Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.43,0:22:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.43,0:22:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:37.27,0:22:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! This is Ishihara, the animal caretaker who transferred away six months ago!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:42.04,0:22:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And this one's Sakamoto, \Nwho vanished two months ago!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.77,0:22:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They too were victims, manipulated by Black Buddha \Nwho preyed on the darkness in their hearts.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:54.36,0:22:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Terror Newspaper Man \Nwas Shimizu-san, the newspaper club president.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.79,0:23:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind those masks were always \Ninnocent, upright people...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.79,0:23:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, when you think about it, \Nwhat's behind it... {? unsure if it's not a double entendre about her underwear}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.60,0:23:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A mystery indeed!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.85,0:23:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, those guys are worse than Black Buddha.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.86,0:23:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.00,0:23:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, come on, don't cry. I'm fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:21.81,0:23:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That was so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.38,0:23:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Damn it all!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.71,0:23:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman again?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.65,0:23:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That accursed loincloth girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.50,0:23:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell is she?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.09,0:23:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,This academy has absolutely no contact \Nwith the secular outside world.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:42.73,0:23:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Vice Principal, are you saying she must be \Nsomeone within the academy?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.73,0:23:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a doubt. \NMost likely one of our female students. {btw this guy is most likely a reference to Tiger Mask's Mister X}{nah I doubt it}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.99,0:23:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Aah, to think such a perfectly rounded peach-like butt \Nalso belongs to a middle school girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:23:56.33,0:23:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She must be gorgeous! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.50,0:24:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, let us employ the full power of the faculty \Nand commence Operation Gautaman Hunt.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.94,0:24:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I ended up becoming the loincloth girl again...
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.85,0:24:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had no choice!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:30.17,0:24:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me, Holy Mary.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:32.96,0:24:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't abandon your lamb. {servant}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:53.04,0:24:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently she's a real beauty.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:54.71,0:24:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and she's got a perfect ass.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:57.13,0:25:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man... I wanna meet that Loincloth Mask too.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:02.97,0:25:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari! Mari!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:05.20,0:25:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:07.04,0:25:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:08.71,0:25:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... I just tripped.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:10.94,0:25:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, you're still as clumsy as ever, Mari.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:13.93,0:25:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:15.70,0:25:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, this afternoon's classes \Ngot changed all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:19.25,0:25:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:19.86,0:25:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's worse, apparently we're having \Na combined PE class... of sumo!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:24.00,0:25:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sumo?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:31.76,0:25:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... dosukoi! {dosukoi}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:33.93,0:25:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oho! A sumo class? \NWell played, Vice Principal.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:38.77,0:25:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman's butt must be somewhere among them.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:43.16,0:25:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But through bloomers and tracksuits, {jerseys}\NI cannot discern the curves very well.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:48.96,0:25:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite right, sir. \NIn that case, our next move will be...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:56.01,0:25:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is kinda embarrassing.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:58.28,0:26:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, it actually suits you. \NHave you never worn one before?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:03.29,0:26:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no! Absolutely not! Never ever!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:06.91,0:26:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why're you getting so defensive?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:09.73,0:26:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,T-That's because...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:11.70,0:26:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I was wondering, why do girls \Nhave to dress like this too?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:15.84,0:26:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, now that you mention it, it is pretty sudden.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:27.60,0:26:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:30.17,0:26:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"What do you think you're doing," you say?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:34.81,0:26:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Stepping into the sumo ring, \Nwhich is off-limits to women,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:38.65,0:26:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and even worse, \Nwearing the sumo belt over one's clothes...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:42.97,0:26:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is utterly outrageous! {女人禁制の土俵へ足を踏み入れあまつさえ服の上からまわしを締めるなど言語道断!!!!}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:46.10,0:26:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you agree, male students?!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:48.92,0:26:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Exactly! Show 'em! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:51.92,0:26:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sumo belts are meant to be worn on bare skin!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:54.42,0:26:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:57.42,0:27:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't up for discussion! \NGirls exposing their butts in public...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:01.72,0:27:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,how could anyone shameless enough \Nto do that even exist?!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:04.67,0:27:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Exactly!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:06.66,0:27:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Shameless...
Dialogue: 10,0:27:11.06,0:27:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoever's got problem with that, step forward!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:22.06,0:27:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent. By speaking pure logic, \Nhe's drawn out the darkness in the boys' hearts.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:27.48,0:27:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now things are unfolding exactly as planned.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:32.00,0:27:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come at me if you dare!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:35.02,0:27:39.76,Thought,,0,0,0,,Lord, going through something that humiliating \Nall by myself was more than enough! {exposing her butt, meaning no else should have to do that}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:39.76,0:27:41.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,Right, Holy Mother?!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:41.80,0:27:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not coming, I'll go get you! {??}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:46.03,0:27:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold the force of Dark Vader!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:48.56,0:27:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! It's raining butts! {nyotaimori = practice of eating sushi or sashimi off an unclad woman's body - no idea why they say that, they're not eating anything off them... yet?}
Dialogue: 10,0:27:52.93,0:27:56.23,Thought,,0,0,0,,I swore I wouldn't transform ever again!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:56.23,0:28:00.69,Thought,,0,0,0,,But I can't just stand by and watch \Neveryone else go through that hell!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:04.91,0:28:05.78,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ah! Here too!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:05.78,0:28:09.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,And there too! \NWhy are all the bathrooms closed?!  {lit: why won't it open}
Dialogue: 10,0:28:10.52,0:28:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:14.54,0:28:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What a disgusting creep.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:16.21,0:28:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And the boys are just as bad.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:17.85,0:28:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't they ashamed of themselves as men of faith?!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:21.53,0:28:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no use, Minami-san. \NLook into their eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:25.32,0:28:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The boys have already been swallowed by the darkness in their hearts.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:28.93,0:28:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Found one!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:32.02,0:28:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:28:33.39,0:28:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally found it.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:35.02,0:28:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go...
Dialogue: 10,0:28:41.11,0:28:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Mari?!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:43.62,0:28:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:28:48.82,0:28:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman, come forth!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:24.99,0:29:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That one? This one?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:26.85,0:29:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:27.65,0:29:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right, thump-thump, like that... What?! {pokupoku = rhythmically (beating, e.g. gong)​}
Dialogue: 10,0:29:30.49,0:29:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:29:32.07,0:29:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as evil exists in this world, \Nthe rage of justice calls to me!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:36.87,0:29:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Butt Attack Punisher Girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:39.62,0:29:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:44.88,0:29:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! The boys' eyes!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:46.85,0:29:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing the glow of Gautaman's butt \Nsnapped them back to their senses!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:51.34,0:29:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:57.64,0:29:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Vader, let's settle this!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:59.83,0:30:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gladly! {dosukoi}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:02.23,0:30:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! You think you can beat me \Nwith strength alone?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:10.46,0:30:13.87,Thought,,0,0,0,,Gautaman's power is filling my body!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:14.50,0:30:17.62,Thought,,0,0,0,,What an overpowering force!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:18.80,0:30:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ew! What's that smell?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:22.21,0:30:25.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ah, this suffocating odor...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:25.59,0:30:28.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,this is the smell of a man's body.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:29.13,0:30:30.11,Thought,,0,0,0,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:30.11,0:30:34.98,Thought,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm being embraced by a man right now! {which is somehow unchristian ig?}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:35.47,0:30:36.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,Almost naked, no less!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:36.64,0:30:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,She's crying! \NGautaman's crying!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:39.90,0:30:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with her?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:41.24,0:30:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:48.64,0:30:51.58,Top,,0,0,0,,Thou shall not commit adultery. {汝・姦淫するなかれ}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:51.58,0:30:54.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,Lord, please forgive me!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:54.41,0:30:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Gautaman's trembling! {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:30:57.01,0:30:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark Vader, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 10,0:30:59.81,0:31:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Tightening the loincloth more
Dialogue: 10,0:31:01.28,0:31:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is having the opposite effect! Loosen it!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:02.64,0:31:03.92,Overlap,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:03.92,0:31:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw her upward!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:05.43,0:31:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Gautaman's spirit shall relax, and with it \Nthe loincloth, causing it to come undone in midair!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:20.77,0:31:22.14,Thought,,0,0,0,,The loincloth...!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:26.44,0:31:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:30.44,0:31:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you now!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:33.45,0:31:35.87,Top,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:35.87,0:31:37.18,Top,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:37.18,0:31:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Secret technique: buttfirst lance! {????????? R1 had "secret technique gladiolus" but I don't see what it has to do with a flower; not in manga}{ブラジング?}
Dialogue: 10,0:31:41.38,0:31:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:54.17,0:31:56.55,Top,,0,0,0,,She did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:31:57.17,0:32:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy was Nakada-san from the sci-fi club!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:00.68,0:32:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He was another victim \Nmanipulated by Black Buddha...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:13.57,0:32:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How unfortunate.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:15.27,0:32:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well, Dark Vader.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:17.83,0:32:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your death shall not be in vain.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:20.83,0:32:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman... Who is she really?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:24.59,0:32:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There has been no mistake.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:26.64,0:32:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,With this butt print that Dark Vader \Nobtained at the cost of his life,
Dialogue: 10,0:32:32.30,0:32:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,we've practically cornered Gautaman already.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:36.34,0:32:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If only that were true. {/I hope it is so}
Dialogue: 10,0:32:40.56,0:32:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is troublesome.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:42.39,0:32:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,To suddenly develop an allergy \Nto the very smell of boys...
Dialogue: 10,0:32:45.96,0:32:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll decorate the classroom with wildflowers. \NHallways too. Then I think I should be okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:51.75,0:32:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your fear of men is only getting worse, isn't it?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:57.34,0:33:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like a little child, Mari.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:01.08,0:33:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:07.97,0:33:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan, hurry!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:12.74,0:33:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:13.94,0:33:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I wasn't paying attention. Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:21.15,0:33:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you get up? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:25.49,0:33:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 10,0:33:26.62,0:33:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies. We collided unexpectedly. \NI didn't mean to startle her.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:32.21,0:33:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. She's just suffering \Nfrom sudden severe androphobia.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:40.34,0:33:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What delicate eyes she has...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:43.64,0:33:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wildflower girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:45.39,0:33:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall never forget you.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:50.80,0:33:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mari?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:54.09,0:33:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been lost in thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:56.40,0:33:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? W-Was I making...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:59.60,0:34:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that kind of face? {meaning she's been thinking about that boy she bumped into and was afraid it'd show through }
Dialogue: 10,0:34:00.77,0:34:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure were!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:02.31,0:34:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your feelings always show on your face.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:04.53,0:34:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be you're thinking about Tobishima-san, \Nthe student council president you bumped into?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:09.90,0:34:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So his name is Tobishima-san...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:12.57,0:34:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:34:12.98,0:34:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, it's not like that at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:15.86,0:34:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with your fear of men, \Nfeelings are another matter, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:20.66,0:34:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how much you like him, \Nyou can't even hold hands or get close! That's so sad.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:25.37,0:34:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it's not like that!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:27.80,0:34:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a devout Christian!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:30.50,0:34:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh please, Christians are allowed \Nto fall in love too, aren't they?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:33.99,0:34:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're acting even more suspicious.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:35.79,0:34:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on, confess your feelings already.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:37.49,0:34:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, I said that's {\i1}not{\i0} it!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:40.23,0:34:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan, you meanie!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:54.74,0:34:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari... you've got a pretty nice body, actually.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:00.08,0:35:03.77,Thought,,0,0,0,,She was like a wildflower in bloom.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:05.70,0:35:09.36,Thought,,0,0,0,,This excitement in my heart... \NThese indescribable feelings...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:09.36,0:35:11.76,Thought,,0,0,0,,This is love.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:11.76,0:35:12.67,Thought,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 10,0:35:12.67,0:35:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The butt print, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:15.71,0:35:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A magnificent butt print. \NTruly a work of art.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:19.68,0:35:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it's not to my personal taste.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:22.85,0:35:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, with this butt print, \Nwe shall uncover Gautaman's true identity.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:26.93,0:35:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Show no mercy! With Black Buddha's prestige \Nat stake, we can't be picky about our methods!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:32.44,0:35:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,A beauty contest?!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:34.92,0:35:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:35:35.98,0:35:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least it has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:38.57,0:35:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, that's not true.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:40.72,0:35:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari, you're cute. Super cute!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:43.22,0:35:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You could enter yourself, Saori-chan.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:45.56,0:35:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's both enter and go for the prize!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:53.99,0:35:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This venue's awfully plain for a beauty contest.
Dialogue: 10,0:35:59.00,0:36:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't really get the judging criteria.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:02.00,0:36:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed up too late. \NDoesn't my face look puffy?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:04.50,0:36:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got more split ends.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:06.01,0:36:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should've cut them shorter?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:07.51,0:36:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That crown is {\i1}so{\i0} mine!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:09.01,0:36:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,T-True enough... {??? idk what she means, what is right - that the judging criteria is unclear?}
Dialogue: 10,0:36:10.35,0:36:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:16.40,0:36:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Could Gautaman really be among them?
Dialogue: 10,0:36:18.96,0:36:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There has been no oversight.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:21.01,0:36:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Every girl nominated has hips \Nmeasuring at least 85 centimeters.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:26.33,0:36:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely enough, Gautaman is among them.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:29.78,0:36:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, for today's Religious Beauty Contest, \NLeaping Into the 21st Century...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:34.23,0:36:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The first and final judging criterion is...
Dialogue: 10,0:36:38.13,0:36:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,this!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:40.79,0:36:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:36:42.29,0:36:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This exquisitely detailed butt print.
Dialogue: 10,0:36:45.19,0:36:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the owner of the butt that perfectly matches this print shall claim today's crown!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:52.05,0:36:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:52.86,0:36:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this, a joke?!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:54.30,0:36:57.31,Thought,,0,0,0,,My butt print... it's a trap!
Dialogue: 10,0:36:57.31,0:37:00.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,This is a trap to find Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:01.81,0:37:05.32,Note,,0,0,0,,[Misora Hibari (1937-1989) = singer and actress; \Nher design here is that of Oozora Hibari, \Na cross-dresser from 1981 manga {\i1}Stop!! Hibari-kun!{\i0}]
Dialogue: 10,0:37:01.81,0:37:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Entry Number One, Misora Hibari!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:05.32,0:37:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! But nobody told me about this kind of judging!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:08.82,0:37:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The platform's too high! My butt won't reach!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:12.32,0:37:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:17.38,0:37:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... H-Hey! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:20.02,0:37:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean it! {??? nanteba?}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:27.06,0:37:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think you can do that, you pervert?! {maybe perverts}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:29.67,0:37:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This butt didn't pass. {/wrong/failed/declined}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:31.27,0:37:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:37:32.43,0:37:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeal, squeal, squeal, squeal... {pi pi pi pi - supposed to represent their cries of indignation}
Dialogue: 10,0:37:34.43,0:37:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop making such a fuss!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:36.29,0:37:40.09,Note,,0,0,0,,[parody of 1963-1969 series of historical dramas {\i1}Nemuri Kyoshiro{\i0}{https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nemuri_Ky%C5%8Dshir%C5%8D#Adaptations}{he is a visual parody of Ichikawa Raizo, the actor who played Nemuri}]
Dialogue: 10,0:37:36.29,0:37:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This Inemuri Kyoshiro won't stay silent forever!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:42.44,0:37:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:37:46.11,0:37:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can no longer escape. Each and every one \Nof you shall press your butt against this print...
Dialogue: 10,0:37:50.94,0:37:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you shall undergo the sacred ritual \Nof butt-print examination.
Dialogue: 10,0:37:54.36,0:37:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, Entry Number Two, Amachi Mari... step up!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:59.49,0:38:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:03.87,0:38:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Stay away!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:07.34,0:38:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wail and beg for mercy!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:09.19,0:38:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You shall now face the curse of your own butt!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:11.61,0:38:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you must resent someone, resent Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:14.69,0:38:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:38:16.01,0:38:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Minami-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:17.01,0:38:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Let go! Saori-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:21.78,0:38:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:23.44,0:38:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mari?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:29.40,0:38:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,M-My wildflower girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:33.82,0:38:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move. If you do, \NI might slice one of your butt cheeks!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:39.28,0:38:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That delicate wildflower-like maiden...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:42.19,0:38:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,couldn't possibly be Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:45.21,0:38:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss? Boss, please wait...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:49.27,0:38:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you prepared?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:53.30,0:38:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough already!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:55.10,0:38:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Saori-chan!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:56.50,0:38:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman will never let \Nthis kind of cruelty slide!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:01.07,0:39:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That is precisely why we are searching for Gautaman.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:04.71,0:39:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So then... is it you?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:08.49,0:39:12.87,Note,,0,0,0,,[Shibaren = shortening of Shibata Renzaburo (1917-1978), \Nthe author of Nemuri Kyoshiro novels]
Dialogue: 10,0:39:08.49,0:39:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,This secret circle butt cutting technique \Nwas passed on to me by Shibaren himself! {lit: shibaren direct transmission (of mystery, skill, secret, etc.), circle butt swordsmanship technique - shibaren is a shortening of shibata renzaburo, somehow - https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Renzabur%C5%8D_Shibata - the author of the novel this guy is from}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:21.54,0:39:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She exceeded the boundaries of the butt print! \NWhat a pitifully oversized backside! {???}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:27.29,0:39:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Saori-chan...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:28.92,0:39:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So embarrassing...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:34.31,0:39:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't breathe...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:35.30,0:39:39.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,I can't... I simply can't... forgive them!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:39.66,0:39:43.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,Mari, that indignation you feel \Nmakes instant transformation possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:43.70,0:39:47.85,Thought,,0,0,0,,Do not hesitate. Now, achieve \Nthe flash transformation! {???? jouchaku / 蒸着 (lit. steam clothing) = vacuum deposition​ - a special term from chemistry, I have no idea what it's supposed to mean as a transformation name, but the point is probably that it's instantaneous like a stamp and not a drawn-out transformation sequence; apparently the same word was used for transformation in https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Space_Sheriff_Gavan but I say fuck it}
Dialogue: 10,0:39:50.31,0:39:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! What's that?!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:52.17,0:39:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:52.82,0:39:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:55.32,0:39:57.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance! Flash transform!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:06.96,0:40:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You...!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:10.79,0:40:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The one and only Butt Attack Punisher Girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:14.30,0:40:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gautaman!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:15.72,0:40:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you rust on my sword! {meaning that she'll become blood on his sword that'll rust }
Dialogue: 10,0:40:22.31,0:40:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Barebutt Sword-catching Technique! {真尻白刃どり - "true ass stopping a sword stroke between one's bare hands"}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:25.57,0:40:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?! {nanja korya?}
Dialogue: 10,0:40:28.32,0:40:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Folding Fan Crush!
Dialogue: 10,0:40:33.52,0:40:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:40:40.49,0:40:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There are 246 female students \Nin this academy named "Mari."
Dialogue: 10,0:40:44.88,0:40:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,To think I doubted that delicate wildflower girl...
Dialogue: 10,0:40:50.11,0:40:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How foolish.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:51.50,0:40:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,An urgent report, sir.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:53.72,0:40:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:56.10,0:40:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pope?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:57.21,0:41:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, embarrassing yourself\N over one mere loincloth girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:01.39,0:41:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So even the Pope was informed...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:03.61,0:41:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! Not even the blink of an ant \Ncould escape the notice of my ears and eyes.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:10.24,0:41:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I grant you one week.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:12.80,0:41:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Bury Gautaman.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:15.19,0:41:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Should you fail, you shall be cast out \Nfrom your position as the boss of Black Buddha.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:20.18,0:41:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, you can consider \Nyour future forever erased!
Dialogue: 10,0:41:23.51,0:41:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If the matter exceeds your ability, \NI myself shall step in.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:26.49,0:41:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my pride as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:28.99,0:41:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I shall dispose of Gautaman \Nwith my own hands...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:31.75,0:41:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Do not forget that vow.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:40.95,0:41:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If I cannot bring down Gautaman...
Dialogue: 10,0:41:44.19,0:41:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that pure and innocent wildflower girl,
Dialogue: 10,0:41:51.08,0:41:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,along with all the women of this academy, \Nwill be thrown into an unjust witch hunt.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:08.62,0:42:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless I defeat Gautaman myself, \Nthe academy's indiscriminate Gautaman hunt
Dialogue: 10,0:42:13.67,0:42:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,will condemn her too to an undeserved martyrdom.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:16.62,0:42:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be burned by its flames!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:19.87,0:42:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But I absolutely will not allow that to happen.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:23.66,0:42:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The name of my beloved is...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:27.13,0:42:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Amachi Mari.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:30.72,0:42:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,These feelings... no one can stop them anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:47.10,0:42:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobishima-senpai...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:49.97,0:42:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,will I ever...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:52.59,0:42:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,see you again?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:46.15,0:43:58.59,Song,,0,0,0,,The echoing footsteps, what on earth will this busy town bring me? {ありのまま君のまま by Noguchi Noriko; even proxyman couldn't find a trace of CD so no lyrics, translating by ear}
Dialogue: 10,0:44:01.97,0:44:14.89,Song,,0,0,0,,I don't care how anyone looks at me anymore, \Nand I can even sleep late in the morning
Dialogue: 10,0:44:15.75,0:44:24.83,Song,,0,0,0,,Even though I don't have time every day, \NI manage to keep up with the city's fast pace somehow {?????}
Dialogue: 10,0:44:24.83,0:44:33.30,Song,,0,0,0,,I go out with a calm, unfazed expression, \Nand my back hidden by my shirt {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:44:33.30,0:44:38.79,Song,,0,0,0,,I know, it doesn't matter... is what I always say
Dialogue: 10,0:44:41.18,0:44:49.24,Song,,0,0,0,,I wish I could make it come true \NIt's something everyone wishes for
Dialogue: 10,0:44:49.24,0:44:54.81,Song,,0,0,0,,I know, this unseen time {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:44:57.07,0:45:05.81,Song,,0,0,0,,I wish, let's search for it, with you being just the way you are
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.81,0:45:08.81,Song,,0,0,0,,
